text: Samtse District (Dzongkha: བསམ་རྩེ་རྫོང་ཁག་; Wylie: Bsam-rtse rdzong-khag; older spelling "Samchi") is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Samtse. There are fifteen village blocks: * Dungtoe Gewog * Dophoogchen Gewog * Duenchukha Gewog * Namgaychhoeling Gewog * Norbugang Gewog * Norgaygang Gewog * Pemaling Gewog * Phuentshogpelri Gewog * Samtse Gewog * Sangngagchhoeling Gewog * Tading Gewog * Tashicholing Gewog * Tendu Gewog * Ugentse Gewog * Yoeseltse Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Samtse District
